Class VisibilityScanDeleteTracker

java.lang.Object

org.apache.hadoop.hbase.security.visibility.VisibilityScanDeleteTracker
All Implemented Interfaces:
DeleteTracker, ShipperListener
@Private public class VisibilityScanDeleteTracker extends ScanDeleteTracker
Similar to ScanDeletTracker but tracks the visibility expression also before deciding if a Cell can be considered deleted
